      "versionNonce": 555451341,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1782675249286,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "algo:\n1. set up directed graph\n2. let's dfs w backtracking, use visited set to detect cycles\n3. we also need to actually return the lists of course order \n-- how?\n\nmaybe we add as we are unraveling dfs, this should handle itself\n(things w no prereqs will add themselves first, then as we clear \nout our dictionary entries of prereqs they are added to the \noutput list)\n\n\n\n\n\n\n ",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "algo:\n1. set up directed graph\n2. let's dfs w backtracking, use visited set to detect cycles\n3. we also need to actually return the lists of course order \n-- how?\n\nmaybe we add as we are unraveling dfs, this should handle itself\n(things w no prereqs will add themselves first, then as we clear \nout our dictionary entries of prereqs they are added to the \noutput list)\n\n\n\n\n\n\n ",
