    {
      "id": "grKW50xhhdCjIux2v6IEf",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 977.6738195381365,
      "y": 105.22620822741453,
      "width": 885.9395141601562,
      "height": 425,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b0M",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 69902339,
      "version": 1745,
      "versionNonce": 640295651,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1782694732000,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "algo:\nwe need some DP table here, but basic is choose/skip algo and take max\n\nset table as [-1] * (n + 2)\n\ndfs (i)\nbase case: i >= len(nums)\n\nskip: table[i + 1], if -1 then call dfs(i + 1) and store\ntake: table[i + 2] + nums[i], if table[i + 2] == -1, call dfs(i + 2) and store\n\ntable[i] = max(skip, table)\nreturn table[i]\n\nnow how to deal w cycle?\nwell we either use 0th idx or we dont, so we can just use house robber i on idx [0, n - 2] \nand idx[1, n - 1] and max",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "algo:\nwe need some DP table here, but basic is choose/skip algo and take max\n\nset table as [-1] * (n + 2)\n\ndfs (i)\nbase case: i >= len(nums)\n\nskip: table[i + 1], if -1 then call dfs(i + 1) and store\ntake: table[i + 2] + nums[i], if table[i + 2] == -1, call dfs(i + 2) and store\n\ntable[i] = max(skip, table)\nreturn table[i]\n\nnow how to deal w cycle?\nwell we either use 0th idx or we dont, so we can just use house robber i on idx [0, n - 2] \nand idx[1, n - 1] and max",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
