      "updated": 1782692716929,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "we would start at the first 2:\nif we choose, then we can't do the 3, so we go to the next 2. however, this is next to the first two (loop), so our val is 2\nif we skip, we do the 3, skip the next 2, and cannot add the 2 after that either (it is next to us)",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "we would start at the first 2:\nif we choose, then we can't do the 3, so we go to the next 2. however, this is next to the first two (loop), so our val is 2\nif we skip, we do the 3, skip the next 2, and cannot add the 2 after that either (it is next to us)",
